  m_text: 'Perfect purity <color="red">cannot</color> be achieved through refinement
    alone.


    - Refinement of purity stops at Pristine.

    - Perfect gems can
    only appear through a <color="green">perfect</color> awakening


    This is
    intentional: Perfect gems are meant to be exceptionally rare.

    Even the most
    refined gem may never become Perfect without luck.'
