  m_text: "Essence is the currency that fuels Gemcraft.\n\n- Gained automatically
    over time\n- Nearby players increase Essence gain (caps at 6 people)\n- Caps
    at 600, so make sure to spent it\n\nCost:\n1 Pull = 25 Essence\n\nYou don\u2019t
    need to do anything - just be around. Hanging out together makes Essence flow
    faster."
