  m_text: "Gemcraft is a passive system where Essence can be used to awake it into
    gemstones while you hang out.\n\n- You gain <color=\"green\">Essence</color>
    over time\n- <color=\"green\">Essence</color> can be spent to pull <color=\"red\">Gemstones</color>\n-
    Depending on the rarity the gem's purity is increased\n- Gemcraft is desigend
    to play along socializing,\n   without requiring all your attention"
