  m_text: "<color=\"green\">Gem Awakening</color> channels your Essence into a gemstone,
    revealing its rarity.\nAwakening gemstones come in familiar rarities:\n  > Common\n 
    > Uncommon\n  > Rare\n  > Epic\n  > Legendary\n  > Perfect\nHigher rarity means
    greater gain for that gem's purity."
